OL,3,CThousands raised for funeral of
OL,4,C'loved' man killed in pub attack
OL,6,FFriends of a man who died following an
OL,7,Fattack outside a pub have raised more
OL,8,Fthan #17,000 to give him the
OL,9,F"incredible send-off" they say he
OL,10,Fdeserves.
OL,12,FBen Wright was assaulted outside
OL,13,FDessie's Place on Liverpool Road in
OL,14,FIrlam shortly before 3:00am on Sunday,
OL,15,F29 March 2026. He was rushed to
OL,16,Fhospital but died from his injuries
OL,17,Ftwo days later.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
