OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775462699
OL,3,CThousands raised for funeral of
OL,4,C'loved' man killed in pub attack
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police have since
OL,7,Flaunched a murder investigation. Three
OL,8,Fmen in their 20s, who were initially
OL,9,Farrested on suspicion of assault, have
OL,10,Fbeen released on bail pending further
OL,11,Fenquiries.
OL,13,FBen's friends have launched a GoFundMe
OL,14,Fpage to support his family and cover
OL,15,Ffuneral costs.
OL,17,FOrganiser Steven Barlow described Ben
OL,18,Fas a man who "truly loved his family
OL,19,Fand his friends" and was happiest when
OL,20,Fthose around him were enjoying
OL,21,Fthemselves.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775462699
OL,3,CThousands raised for funeral of
OL,4,C'loved' man killed in pub attack
OL,6,F"He had a gift for bringing people
OL,7,Ftogether and making everyone feel
OL,8,Fwelcome, and that is something we will
OL,9,Fnever forget," Mr Barlow wrote.
OL,11,F"Anyone who knew Ben will have at
OL,12,Fleast one special memory of him, and
OL,13,Fwe want to come together to make sure
OL,14,Fhe gets an incredible send-off that
OL,15,Ftruly celebrates his life and
OL,16,Feverything he meant to us."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
