OL,3,CThousands raised for funeral of
OL,4,C'loved' man killed in pub attack
OL,6,FThe pub where the attack took place,
OL,7,FDessie's Place, also shared a moving
OL,8,Ftribute to Mr. Wright, revealing that
OL,9,Fhe was a former member of staff and a
OL,10,Fbeloved regular.
OL,12,FIn a statement posted to Facebook, the
OL,13,Fpub said: "Ben wasn't just someone who
OL,14,Fworked with us, he was part of our
OL,15,Ffamily. He loved the pub, the people
OL,16,Fin it, and all the regulars who walked
OL,17,Fthrough those doors."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775462699
OL,3,CThousands raised for funeral of
OL,4,C'loved' man killed in pub attack
OL,6,F"His smile, his laugh, and his
OL,7,Fpresence brought so much life into the
OL,8,Fplace, and it simply won't be the same
OL,9,Fwithout him. He was one of us... not
OL,10,Fjust a regular, but one of the best."
OL,12,FAll remaining funds from the
OL,13,Ffundraising campaign will be given to
OL,14,FMr. Wright's immediate family to
OL,15,Fsupport them during what friends have
OL,16,Fdescribed as an "incredibly difficult
OL,17,Ftime."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
